{"tid":690362,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得有條打靶仔叫羅鈞滿","createTime":"2018-06-04T20:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T01:37:31.000Z","uid":159798,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a4afed21041850c17aac74d7c2a624173df957c3","tid":690362,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T20:19:37.000Z","msg":"舊菜都嫁人喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/最新娛聞/張文采-10月嫁消防員2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%A8%9B%E8%81%9E%2F%E5%BC%B5%E6%96%87%E9%87%87-10%E6%9C%88%E5%AB%81%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E5%93%A12%2F&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5e19c102\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/最新娛聞/張文采-10月嫁消防員2/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就順便search下羅生最近撈緊乜<br />\n對上一篇有關佢發展動向嘅新聞已經係一年前<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/97203/羅鈞滿離開無綫全力北上-洗-負評王-底-演活人生中最正氣角色\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F97203%2F%E7%BE%85%E9%88%9E%E6%BB%BF%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%8C%97%E4%B8%8A-%E6%B4%97-%E8%B2%A0%E8%A9%95%E7%8E%8B-%E5%BA%95-%E6%BC%94%E6%B4%BB%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E6%AD%A3%E6%B0%A3%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=af8050b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/97203/羅鈞滿離開無綫全力北上-洗-負評王-底-演活人生中最正氣角色</a><br />\n<br />\n藝人羅鈞滿負面新聞纏身，雖然在TVB神劇《天與地》演年輕版鼓佬，鮮明的角色立刻吸引到觀眾的注意，但在劇集背後他個人的生活言論備受非議。先有在微博自嘲「三線藝人」力撐女友張文采；再有<span style=\"color: red;\">參加歌唱比賽節目《星夢傳奇》頻頻走音被笑；後有背女友偷食又醉駕被捕，醜事一籮籮，上年本來還有7年合約在身，但雙方決定和平解約。但羅鈞滿在香港劣評如潮，被網民推舉成「負評王」</span>，那麼他解約後究竟去了哪裏工作呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原來解約之後羅鈞滿簽約「幸運星娛樂文化有限公司」，主力在大陸發展</span>，第一部接拍的是大陸懸疑網劇《大清神捕2》，第一次參與演出已經擔任皇帝角色，認真威水，似乎離開TVB之後星途更耀眼。<br />\n昨日<span style=\"color: red;\">羅鈞滿又上載機票照片，表示自己準備去橫店拍劇，回大陸工作才沒多久，又大晒商務客位機票，原來他是去客串《笑澳江湖》</span>，即使是客串角色亦未有影響他的好心情，他說：「橫店第一擊，《笑澳江湖》開機儀式，演活人生中最最最正氣的角色！」看來羅鈞滿很適合大陸發展，大陸觀眾對他的印象還不錯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想關心佢上大陸發展左兩年，成績如何<br />\n<br />\n先去佢微博，嘩萬人迷喎，平均每篇有4, 50個like<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/u/1722847404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fu%2F1722847404&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=576ad62b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/u/1722847404</a><br />\n<br />\n睇埋百度，一年得幾個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=罗钧满&amp;mo_device=1&amp;pn=0&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Ff%3Fkw%3D%E7%BD%97%E9%92%A7%E6%BB%A1%26mo_device%3D1%26pn%3D0%26&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=40b0c1cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=罗钧满&amp;mo_device=1&amp;pn=0&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n連佢入左嗰間幸福星，都係一年前停左update了<br />\n<a href=\"http://nstar.com.hk/category/news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnstar.com.hk%2Fcategory%2Fnews%2F&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBpzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=01ffdb03\" target=\"_blank\">http://nstar.com.hk/category/news/</a><br />\n<br />\n除此之外完全search唔到佢最近參演過咩劇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">說好的發展呢？？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我最好奇係佢呢一年究竟點樣維生？"},{"pid":"afbb77ea07f0a5c85b9ba3614b98160160f533a9","tid":690362,"uid":35451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T20:47:58.000Z","msg":"淨係記得膠水頭"},